Link is a hyperlink in [[Wiklo]].

<code>{{!((}}Wiklo{{!))}}</code> produces:
[[Wiklo]]

<code>{{!((}}Wiklo|Alt Text{{!))}}</code> produces:
[[Wiklo|Alt Text]]

<code>{{!((}}Unknown Page|Alt Text{{!))}}</code> produces:
[[Unknown Page|Alt Text]] (A link that does not exist)

<code>{{!((}}Link{{!))}}</code> produces:
[[Link]] (Self-link)

<code>{{!((}}http://example.com|example.com{{!))}}</code> produces:
[[http://example.com|example.com]] (External link)